<section class="Process">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2>How we work</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p class="section-header-desc">No vague timelines. No disappearing after kickoffs. No invoices for work you didn't agree to. Here's exactly how a project runs.</p>

            <div class="process-steps">
                <div class="step">
                    <p>01. Discovery Call</p>
                    <p>A deep dive focused 15-minute conversation to dive into your goals, users and constraints so we build the right thing, not just anything.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="step">
                    <p>02. Scoped Proposal</p>
                    <p>Clearly written document: deliverables, timeline, pricing — no vague estimates. You know exactly what you're signing before any money moves.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="step">
                    <p>03. Design Sprints</p>
                    <p>Clickable prototypes before building anything. You approve the experience. What you see is what gets built.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="step">
                    <p>04. Agile Build Sprints</p>
                    <p>Weekly demos and transparent progress tracking. No black boxes, no "it's nearly ready" for six weeks.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="step">
                    <p>05. QA & Launch</p>
                    <p>Tested across devices, browsers, and load scenarios. We release in stages so launch day is quiet — which means everything worked.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="step">
                    <p>06. Growth Support</p>
                    <p>Post-launch support, monitoring, perfomance tuning and a retainer option for ongoing features. We're not a project shop — we become part of your team.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>